    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Coda /s/ in Puerto Rico ",
          "textSize": "heading-four"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "The Spanish spoken by Puerto Ricans features a significant amount of /s/ reduction. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
