    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "D-Deletion is also a frequent feature in reggaetón production and is typically transcribed orthographically in online lyrics with a combination of accented vowels (e.g., crecía) or complete omission (e.g., lao) "
